name: Discord
author: Discord Inc.
description: All-in-one voice and text chat for gamers that's free, secure, and works on both your desktop and phone.

wine.general: Discord has a native Linux client (Debian, Flatpak, Snap). If you must use Wine, ensure you have corefonts installed.

name: Spotify
author: Spotify AB
description: Spotify is a digital music service that gives you access to millions of songs.

wine.general: Native Linux client is highly recommended via Flatpak or the official repository.

name: VS Code
author: Microsoft
description: Code editing. Redefined. Free. Built on open source. Runs everywhere.

wine.general: Native Linux client available for all major distros. Wine not recommended for VS Code.
